* !asset #23036751: {{raffina_(puyopuyo) puyopuyo_tetris|Puyopuyo Tetris}}

h4. Trivia
* Formerly known as <b>Raffine</b> prior to 2017, coinciding with the English localization of <i>Puyo Puyo Tetris</i>.
* Her name is French for 'refined'; ironic given her often haughty nature.
* She's voiced by Namiki Noriko in Japanese and Erica Lindbeck in English.

